    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have got to see this absolute beauty. It\u2019s in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It has been pampered since day one and drives like a total dream. If you are looking for a ride that is practically flawless and ready for its next adventure, this is the one for you. Drop me a message and let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
